Package itunesq

Class ITQTableViewRowComparator

java.lang.Object
itunesq.ITQTableViewRowComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparator<Object>
public class ITQTableViewRowComparator extends Object implements Comparator<Object>
Class that compares two table view rows during a sort operation. This gets control when the user clicks on a column header in a table of tracks or artists. Stolen without remorse from Pivot code, cleaned up to meet my standards, and modified to handle columns that contain numerical data.
Author:
Jon
